@page "/"

<PageTitle>Overview</PageTitle>

<div class="space-y-6">
	<div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
		<p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-500">Monitoring workspace</p>
		<h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Stay ahead of processing drift</h1>
		<p class="muted max-w-2xl">
			XTMon keeps your operational signals visible: database size, disk pressure, and the health of
			your processing pipeline. Refresh on demand and keep teams aligned with a single source of truth.
		</p>
		<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
			<a class="primary-button" href="monitoring">Open dashboard</a>
			<span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-white px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-200">
				SQL Server localhost:1433
			</span>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
		<div class="stat-card">
			<p class="stat-label">Live visibility</p>
			<p class="stat-value">Single refresh</p>
			<p class="muted mt-2">Pulls the latest metrics from your stored procedure when you need them.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="stat-card">
			<p class="stat-label">Flexible schema</p>
			<p class="stat-value">Any columns</p>
			<p class="muted mt-2">The dashboard adapts to whichever fields the procedure returns.</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="surface">
		<div class="flex flex-col gap-3 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-between">
			<div>
				<p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-500">Next steps</p>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Connect your production insights</h2>
				<p class="muted mt-2 max-w-2xl">
					Update the connection string with your SQL login and keep expanding the stored procedure
					output to include pipeline KPIs such as batch latency, failures, and queue depth.
				</p>
			</div>
			<a class="primary-button" href="monitoring">Review data</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
